-30]] || [[File:FestiveFireworks2018-02.jpg|150px]] || {{USSR}} || Howitzer || 9 || Used only as ceremonial [[howitzer]]. More were sold to Afghanistan.\n|-\n! style=\"align: center; background: lavender;\" colspan=\"7\" | [[Engineering Vehicles]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|[[OT-90|AMB-S]] || [[File:OT-90 AMB-S.jpg|150px]] || {{CZS}}<br>{{SVK}} ||Armoured military [[ambulance]]|| ? || Based on a [[BVP-1]] chassis\n|- valign=\"top\" \n| [[OT-90|VPV]] || [[File:BREM-2 in Kubinka.jpg|150px]] || {{CZS}} || [[Armoured recovery vehicle]] || ? || \n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[T-72 operators and variants#Former Czechoslovakia|VT-72]] || [[File:BREM-1 - ETIF-2010 (1).jpg|150px]] || {{USSR}}<br>{{CZS}} || [[Armoured recovery vehicle]] || ? ||\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[T-54/55 operators and variants#Former Czechoslovakia|VT-55A]] || [[File:IMG 2219 - Flickr - Al Jazeera English.jpg|150px]] || {{USSR}} <br> {{CZS}} || [[Armoured recovery vehicle]] || ? || \n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Tatra 815|AV-15]] || [[File:Tatra 815 AV 15 pic2.JPG|150px]] || {{CZS}} || [[Armoured recovery vehicle]] || ? || \n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[T-55 variants#Slovakia|UOS 155 Belarty]] || [[File:UOS 155 Belarty 2.jpg|150px]] || {{SVK}} || [[Demining]], [[Combat engineering vehicle]] || ? || Based on a [[T-55]] chassis\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|[https://web.archive.org/web/20160402052357/http://bozena.eu/sk/ Bo\u017eena 3 Bo\u017eena 4 Bo\u017eena 5] || [[File:Tral bozena.jpg|150px]] || {{SVK}} || [[Demining|Demining Mechanical Clearance]] || ? || Remote-controlled self-propelled mine roller \n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[T-54/55#Operators and variants#Former Czechoslovakia|MT-55A]] || [[File:Park of Military History Pivka - MT-55 bridgelayer.jpg|150px]] || {{CZS}}<br>{{SVK}} || [[Armoured vehicle-launched bridge]] || 19 || \n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Tatra 815|PM-55]] |||| {{CZS}} || [[Armoured vehicle-launched bridge]] || ? || \n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Tatra 815|AM-50]] || [[File:Mostn\u00ed automobil AM-50 pic1.JPG|150px]] || {{CZS}}