aption=The coat of arms\n|start_date=1993 - present\n|country={{flag|Slovakia}}\n|current_form=January 1, 1993\n|command_structure= [[Armed Forces of the Slovak Republic]]\n|disbanded=\n|branch=[[Armed Forces of the Slovak Republic]]\n|garrison= ''Velite\u013estvo Pozemn\u00fdch s\u00edl OS SR'' - [[Tren\u010d\u00edn]]\n|garrison_label= Command HQ\n<!-- Commanders -->\n|commander1=[[Major General]] Jindrich Joch\n|commander1_label=Commander\n|commander2=\n|commander2_label=\n|commander3=\n|commander3_label=\n<!-- Insignia -->\n|identification_symbol= [[Image:Slovak Army Roundel.svg|150px]] \n|identification_symbol_label= Roundel\n|identification_symbol_2=\n|identification_symbol_2_label=\n}}\nThe '''Slovak Ground Forces''', also known as the '''Slovak Army''', is the land specialized service branch of the [[Slovak Armed Forces]].\n\n== Structure ==\n{{Location map+ | Slovakia | float=right | width=560 | relief = 1| places=\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Tren\u010d\u00edn]]</small> | lat = 48.891944 | long = 18.036667 |position=left|mark=Green pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Topo\u013e\u010dany]]</small> | lat = 48.554167 | long = 18.146944 |position=left|mark=Green pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small></small> | lat = 48.554167 | long = 18.206944 |position=left|mark=Purple pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Martin, Slovakia|Martin]]</small> | lat = 49.065 | long = 18.89 |position=left|mark=Pink pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small></small> | lat = 49.065 | long = 18.95 |position=left|mark=Purple pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Nitra]]</small> | lat = 48.306944 | long = 18.086389 |position=right|mark=Pink pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Levice]]</small> | lat = 48.216389 | long = 18.608056 |position=right|mark=Pink pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Ro\u017e\u0148ava]]</small> | lat = 48.658333 | long = 20.500833 |position=left|mark=Yellow pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small></small> | lat = 48.658333 | long = 20.560833 |position=left|mark=Brown pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Sere\u010f]]</small> | lat = 48.283333 | long = 17.733333 |position=left|mark=Black pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Pre\u0161ov]]</small> | lat = 49 | long = 21.21 |position=left|mark=Green pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small></small> | lat = 49 | long = 21.27 |position=left|mark=Orange pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small></small> | lat = 49.04 | long = 21.24 |position=left|mark=Blue 0080ff pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Trebi\u0161ov]]</small> | lat = 48.627778 | long = 21.68 |position=left|mark=DeepPink pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small></small> | lat = 48.627778 | long = 21.75 |position=left|mark=Lightgreen pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Michalovce]]</small> | lat = 48.755278 | long = 21.90 |position=left|mark=Pink pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small></small> | lat = 48.755278 | long = 21.97 |position=left|mark=Yellow pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Slia\u010d Airport|Slia\u010d]]</small> | lat = 48.637778 | long = 19.133889 |position=right|mark=Blue 0080ff pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[Malacky Air Base|Malacky]]</small> | lat = 48.401944 | long = 17.118333 |position=right|mark=Blue 0080ff pog.svg}}\n{{Location map~ | Slovakia | background = white |label = <small>[[