avy.pravda.sk/domace/clanok/429771-vlada-schvalila-1-2-miliardy-eur-na-nakup-obrnenych-vozidiel/#|archive-date=2017-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[BVP-1]] || [[File:Slovakia army 888.jpg|150px]] || {{USSR}}<br>{{CZS}} ||[[Infantry Fighting Vehicle|IFV]]|| 69 || 236 in storage. Will be replaced by IFV [[Patria AMV|BOV 8x8]] or modernised to BVP-M level.\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[OT-90]] || [[File:BAHNA 2018 - 164.jpg|150px]] || {{CZS}} ||[[Armoured Personnel Carrier|APC]]|| 60 || Main armoured personnel carrier of Slovak army.\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| '''BVP-M''' || [[File:Obrnene Vozidlo.jpg|150px]] || {{SVK}} ||[[Infantry Fighting Vehicle|IFV]]|| 17<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.armadninoviny.cz/slovenska-armada-prevzala-modernizovana-bojova-vozidla-pechoty.html|title=Slovensk\u00e1 arm\u00e1da p\u0159evzala modernizovan\u00e1 bojov\u00e1 vozidla p\u011bchoty|access-date=2018-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180731031526/http://www.armadninoviny.cz/slovenska-armada-prevzala-modernizovana-bojova-vozidla-pechoty.html#|archive-date=2018-07-31|url-status=live}}</ref> || Slovak modernised [[BVP-1]] by 2018 with remote controlled turret TURRA 30 and new communication systems, more BVP-1 to be upgraded to BVP-M level.\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Patria AMV|BOV 8x8]] || [[File:Pansarterr\u00e4ngbil 360 Revinge 2015-2.jpg|150px]] || {{FIN}}<br>{{SVK}} ||[[Infantry Fighting Vehicle|IFV]]|| 0 (81 on order<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aktuality.sk/clanok/545234/rezort-obrany-ukazal-nove-obrnene-vozidlo/|title=Rezort obrany uk\u00e1zal nov\u00e9 obrnen\u00e9 vozidlo 8x8|last=Azet.sk|access-date=2017-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224213620/https://www.aktuality.sk/clanok/545234/rezort-obrany-ukazal-nove-obrnene-vozidlo/#|archive-date=2017-12-24|url-status=live}}</ref>) || Slovak wheeled IFV based on [[Patria AMV|Patria AMV<sup>XP</sup>]] will be delivered between 2018 and 2024.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.combatandsurvival.c